v 2.0
Large code rewrites and speed optimizations
Lots of bug fixes along with UI tweaks
Support for user defined folder structure, for storing books
Advanced filter for book filtering
Filter parameters can be saved as presets and accessed via single click
More fields for editing book information
Book can have multiple categories assigned
Categories are automatically extracted from added books (epub and mobi)
Storing book data changed from serialized .dat files into a SQLite database, which is much faster and cleaner solution
Included german translation (translated by ChrisK91)

v 1.0
First pre-release of the application
